                    "action_type": {
                        "type": "stat_block_section",
                        "subtype": "action_type",
                        "name": "One Action"
                    },
                    "frequency": "once per day",
                    "effect": "You direct a quick bit of insulting mockery at a creature who can understand you that\u2019s within earshot. If your next action is to cast a mental spell that targets only that creature, that creature takes a \u20131 item penalty to any saving throw against the spell and, regardless of the result of the saving throw, becomes off-guard until the start of your next turn.",
